&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="3-opencv-를-이용해서-동영상-실행시켜보기">3. opencv 를 이용해서 동영상 실행시켜보기&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">cv2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">video_path&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;tracking_myidol/dumbi_dumbdi.mp4&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">cap&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">VideoCapture&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">video_path&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">ret&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cap&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">read&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">imshow&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;img&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">while&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cap&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">isOpened&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">():&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">ret&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cap&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">read&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="ow">not&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">ret&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">exit&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">imshow&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;img&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">waitKey&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mi">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">==&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">ord&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;q&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">):&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">break&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">17&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="4-roi-setting">4. ROI Setting&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>ROI (Region of Interest)
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>관심 영역, 영상처리할 때 쓰는 보편적인 용어&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">ret&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cap&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">read&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">namedWindow&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Select Window&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">imshow&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Select Window&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">rect&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">selectROI&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Select Window&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">fromCenter&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="bp">False&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">showCrosshair&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="bp">True&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">destroyWindow&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Select Window&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>동영상 제일 처음 frame을 불러와서 cv2.selectROI 를 이용해 처음에 ROI 를 세팅할 수 있는 창을 만든다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="5-tracker">5. tracker&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>user가 선택한 ROI를 rect 라는 변수에 저장을 하는데, 이를 계속해서 추적하는 obejct tracker가 필요하다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c1"># init tracker&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">tracker&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">TrackerCSRT_create&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">tracker&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">init&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">rect&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">while&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cap&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">isOpened&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">():&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">ret&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cap&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">read&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="ow">not&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">ret&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">exit&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">success&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">box&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">tracker&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">update&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">left&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">top&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">w&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">h&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">list&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">map&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">int&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">box&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">))&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">rectangle&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">pt1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">left&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">top&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">),&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">pt2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">left&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">+&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">w&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">top&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">+&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">h&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">),&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">17&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">color&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mi">255&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">255&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">255&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">),&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">18&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">thickness&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mi">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">19&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">20&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">imshow&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;img&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">21&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">waitKey&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mi">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">==&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">ord&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;q&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">):&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">22&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">break&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">23&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>이렇게 하면 Select Window 창에서 선택된 ROI를 계속해서 tracking 하는 것을 볼 수 있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="6-예상되는-문제점">6. 예상되는 문제점&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>첫 frame에 원하는 인물이 나오지 않을 경우 다음 frame으로 넘길 수 있는 기능이 필요 (2020.08.17 해결)
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>while loop으로 q 외에 다른 키를 누를 경우 frame 넘길 수 있게 처리함.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>그리고 rect가 없을 경우 (0,0,0,0) 의 값을 갖는데 bounding box가 (0,0,0,0) 일 경우는 없다고 판단해서 합이 0이 아니면 break로 while loop 을 break 시킴.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">namedWindow&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Select Window&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">while&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cap&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">isOpened&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">():&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">i&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">+=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">1&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">print&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">i&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">ret&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cap&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">read&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">imshow&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Select Window&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">key&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">waitKey&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mi">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1"># Quit when &amp;#39;q&amp;#39; is pressed&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">key&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">==&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">ord&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;q&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">):&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">break&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">rect&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">selectROI&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Select Window&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">img&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">fromCenter&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="bp">False&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">showCrosshair&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="bp">True&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">print&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">rect&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">sum&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">rect&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">!=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">0&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">destroyWindow&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Select Window&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">break&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>처음 ROI 설정 할 경우 앉은 상태에서 시작할 때, 일어나는 사람의 전체 size를 tracking 하지 못함&lt;/li>
&lt;li>인물이 다른 인물에 가려져서 안보일 경우 어떻게 처리해야 할지.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="7-전체코드">7. 전체코드&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">cv2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">video_path&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;tracking_myidol/dumbi_dumbdi.mp4&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">cap&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">VideoCapture&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">video_path&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">cap&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">set&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">cv2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">CAP_PROP_POS_FRAMES&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">80&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>
